03/04/85 add_anon

Syntax as a command:  add_anon Project_id initproc homedir {password}


Function:  adds an anonymous user to an undelegated project; the
accounting administrator assigns this user a home directory and an
initial procedure and can also assign a password if he wishes.


Arguments:
Project_id
   is the name of the project under which the anonymous user is to be
   registered.
initproc
   is the name of the process overseer.
homedir
   is the pathname of the anonymous user's home directory.
password
   is the password assigned to the anonymous user.
